    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to QiAlly</h1>
        <p>This portal is your **HQ for the project**. Every file, task, and message lives here so you never lose track.</p>

        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <p>QiAlly builds and manages websites with clarity, structure, and ongoing support.</p>

        <h2>What We Do</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Design and launch your website</li>
            <li>Keep the process organized in clear steps</li>
            <li>Provide ongoing support through this portal</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>What We Don't Do</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Add endless extras outside of scope</li>
            <li>Promise 24-hour miracle turnarounds</li>
            <li>Write your content from scratch if you never upload it</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>What We Expect From You</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Upload files promptly</li>
            <li>Communicate inside this portal</li>
            <li>Give clear, consolidated feedback</li>
            <li>Respect timelines so the project doesn’t stall</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How To Use This Portal</h2>
        <div class="section-box">
            <ul>
                <li>**Tasks:** Action items for you and us</li>
                <li>**Files:** Upload and download documents</li>
                <li>**Messages:** All communication threads stay here</li>
                <li>**Forms:** Fill out structured questionnaires or feedback</li>
                <li>**Status:** Current stage + next milestone</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <h1>Stage 1 Tasks</h1>
        <p>By completing these, you ensure you've read the rules, can navigate, and are ready to proceed to Intake & Onboarding.</p>

        <div class="task">
            <strong>Task 1: Read QiAlly 101</strong>
            <p>Quick intro to who we are, what we do, and how this portal works.</p>
            <p>✅ Please also review the QiAlly 101 page in the portal. Mark complete once read.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="task">
            <strong>Task 2: Confirm Understanding</strong>
            <p>Check the box or acknowledge here that you’ve read QiAlly 101 and understand how we work together.</p>
            <p class="requirement">Requirement: client mark complete. Optional: add checklist items like “I understand portal use” / “I know how to send files”.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="task">
            <strong>Task 3: Meet Your Portal</strong>
            <p>Explore the tabs in your portal:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Welcome (this page)</li>
                <li>Tasks (to-dos)</li>
                <li>Files (upload/download)</li>
                <li>Messages (for comms)</li>
                <li>Forms (Discovery & Feedback)</li>
                <li>Status (where we are in the project)</li>
            </ul>
            <p>✅ Mark this task complete once you’ve clicked around.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="task">
            <strong>Task 4: Say Hello</strong>
            <p>Open a Message thread and just say hi. This ensures you know how to send messages in the portal.</p>
            <p class="requirement">Requirement: client message before task completion.</p>
